tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PatientResponses (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    treatment_id INT NOT NULL,
    response_score INT,
    response_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Teleoncologists(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (treatment_id) REFERENCES Treatments(id)
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    patient_age INT,
    patient_gender VARCHAR(10),
    treatment_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE Responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    treatment_id INT,
    response_date DATE,
    response_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    diagnosis VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE Treatments (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    treatment_id INT,
    treatment_name VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT,
    cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE PatientResponses (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    treatment_id INT,
    response VARCHAR(100),
    response_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE PatientData (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255),
    cancer_type VARCHAR(100),
    treatment_id INT,
    response_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE TreatmentPlan (
    treatment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    treatment_name VARCHAR(255),
    treatment_description VARCHAR(500),
    treatment_duration INT,
    treatment_cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE PatientHistory (
    patient_id INT,
    treatment_id INT,
    treatment_date DATE,
    side_effects VARCHAR(500),
    PRIMARY KEY (patient_id, treatment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE TreatmentResponse (
    patient_id INT,
    treatment_id INT,
    response_score INT,
    response_date DATE,
    feedback VARCHAR(500),
    PRIMARY KEY (patient_id, treatment_id)
);
